text: Eleni Ttakka (born 3 March 1996) is a Cypriot footballer who plays as a goalkeeper and has appeared for the Cyprus women's national team. ==Career== Ttakka has been capped for the Cyprus national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Cypriot women's footballers Category:Cyprus women's international footballers Category:Women's association football goalkeepers
